\subsection convection Convection

Class probability for convective precipitation is obtained with \c --pConv command. 

\~exec
FILE=volume.h5 PROD=pConv,25,3,2,20 QUANTITY=PROB ./make-image-product.sh #exec
\~
\include pConv.exm


\image html  pConv-PROB-panel.png "Convection product and its quality field." 
